@node main "Massive - Documentation"


 Massive
 © by Wolfgang Lug



In case that you want to start Massive from a Shell:
First "cd" to Massive's directory, then type "stack 10000" and
hit return.  THIS IS IMPORTANT!  Otherwise you'll get errors like
"Modula-2 Laufzeitfehler / Stapel Überlauf" (= stack overflow).



